  <header><div class="wrap"><a href="index.html">COCOABRIDGE</a> &nbsp; <a href="product.html">Products</a> &nbsp; <a href="services.html">Services</a> &nbsp; <a href="contact.html">Contact</a></div></header>
  <main>
    <section class="hero"><div class="wrap"><p>International agricultural commodity trade</p><h1>Agricultural Export Services From Cameroon for Cocoa and Coffee Buyers</h1><p>COCOABRIDGE coordinates sourcing, quality control, traceability, documentation and logistics for international buyers seeking reliable cocoa and coffee exports from Cameroon.</p><a class="btn-main" href="contact.html">Discuss Export Needs</a><a class="btn-alt" href="services.html">View Main Services</a></div></section>
    <section class="band"><div class="wrap two"><article><h2>Export Support From Inquiry to Shipment</h2><p>Our export process starts with buyer requirements and moves through availability review, sample planning, quality checks, packaging, paperwork and shipment coordination. The goal is straightforward: help qualified buyers move cocoa and coffee from origin to destination with fewer surprises.</p></article><aside class="card"><h2>Core Commodities</h2><ul><li>Cameroon cocoa beans</li><li>Arabica coffee beans</li><li>Robusta coffee beans</li><li>Selected cocoa derivatives</li></ul></aside></div></section>
    <section><div class="wrap"><h2>Service Areas</h2><div class="grid"><article class="card"><h3>Sourcing</h3><p>Origin sourcing from vetted farmer groups, cooperatives and supply partners.</p></article><article class="card"><h3>Quality Assurance</h3><p>Moisture checks, grading, lot review, sampling and buyer specification alignment.</p></article><article class="card"><h3>Export Compliance</h3><p>Commercial documents, origin paperwork, phytosanitary support and customs coordination.</p></article><article class="card"><h3>International Logistics</h3><p>Packaging, warehouse handling, container loading and port or freight communication.</p></article><article class="card"><h3>Traceability</h3><p>Lot-level sourcing records to support buyer confidence and supply chain transparency.</p></article><article class="card"><h3>Buyer Support</h3><p>Quote handling, sample requests, contract planning and long-term supply communication.</p></article></div></div></section>
    <section class="band"><div class="wrap"><h2>Start With the Right Page</h2><div class="grid"><article class="card"><h3>Cameroon Cocoa Exporter</h3><a href="landing-cameroon-cocoa-exporter.html">Source cocoa beans</a></article><article class="card"><h3>Arabica Coffee Supplier</h3><a href="landing-arabica-coffee-supplier.html">Source Arabica</a></article><article class="card"><h3>Robusta Coffee Supplier</h3><a href="landing-robusta-coffee-supplier.html">Source Robusta</a></article></div></div></section>
  </main>
